These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, kiwi, peach, eggplant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, gospel, soul, reggae
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, fish, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, train, car
 1. the person driving the helicopter is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person eating peach is the fan of soul##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 8. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the fan of soul##5
 9. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
11. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | eggplant     | kiwi   | mango | peach |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | trance    | reggae   | soul    |
| Pet           | fish       | rabbit   | horse   | hamster     |
| Transport     | helicopter       | scooter | car  | train      |

