.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, juice, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, documentary, musical, western
4 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, turtle, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, tram, airplane, van
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching western movies and the person drinking mirinda##2
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
 9. the owner of the mouse is the person watching western movies##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
11. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda       | hot-chocolate | sprite     | juice     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary      | romance       | western | musical |
| Pet           | turtle       | chinchilla    | mouse     | goat         |
| Transport     | van | airplane     | train     | tram       |

