 2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 3. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
 4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is between the fan of r&b and the fan of funk##2
 7. the fan of metal is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cabbage    | potato      | grapefruit   | pineapple |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | fantasy | drama | musical  |
