 4. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 6. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 7. the person drinking 7up is between the fan of disco and the person drinking juice##2
 8. the teacher is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
10. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
11. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
12. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
13. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
