 3. the thai is in an odd position##4
 4. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 5. the person eating strawberry is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 8. the russian is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 9. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
10. the person eating tomato is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the spanish##3
12. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
13. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
