 4. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 7. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
