12. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | lemonade | milk   | cola          |
| Food          | apricot    | pear        | corn     | cauliflower          |
| Job           | freelancer | teacher        | musician | pilot |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | comedy     | spy      | mystery        |

