.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, lemonade, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, coach, dressmaker, analyst
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, superhero, animation, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, tram, van
 1. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 3. the analyst is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the coach is between the dressmaker and the person watching musical movies##2
 6. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the dressmaker is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the van##1
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person driving the van is on the right of the scientist##1
13. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | cola      | sprite | fanta     |
| Job           | analyst   | scientist  | coach        | dressmaker |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | musical     | animation      | superhero   |
| Transport     | bus | tram | van          | helicopter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cranberry, peach, papaya
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, analyst, manager, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, zombie, sports, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, r&b, jazz, ambient
 1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
 2. the fan of ambient is the person eating avocado##1
 3. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
 4. the musician is in an even position##4
 5. the analyst is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 6. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
 7. the manager is the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
11. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5
12. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | avocado | peach  | papaya    | cranberry       |
| Job           | analyst  | accountant | manager | musician  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | sports   | musical  | family     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | jazz    | r&b        | trance |

 